text: Cathexis vitticollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Zajciw in 1967. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Cathexis vitticollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1967
